Text: You must ask yourself: are you feeling lucky?
Show me your rage, your rancor!
You'll win no prizes at this rate!
Folly or fortune? Which will it be?
Come to play, have you? Then let's begin!

By my words find riches or ruin.
The choice is yours.

What stumbles and flails?
The burned man.

What comes unto me?
The trapped.

What flees my reach?
The doomed man.

What stands alone?
The dead oak.

What stand together?
Walls turned to ash.
Yes... This is what I longed to feel once more...
Long ago, I fought for honor...for glory...
Tiny warrior... I sense in thee a kindred spirit.
Thou hath reawoken me to the thrill of battle!
The aetheric ice! It's powered some kind of...evolution.

We have to break them.
Break them now!
Yes, the creatures appear thoroughly pulverized.
And the reactor seems none the worse for wear. Thank you!

Professor Gilly!
It was a near thing...
We shall have to rethink our experiment protocol from the ground up.
Understood! I'll start drafting improvements at once!
They've grown too powerful. We withdraw for now...
Naught remaineth for me but to sink into oblivion...
Many thanks, friend. If I'd gone myself, I'd have ended up as some gaja's supper.
If I'm going to risk my life for this job, I want double the coin. Back to town it is, then!
BEHIND EVERY SMILE...IS DEATH AND ANNIHILATION!
So glorious as to inspire a new song, methinks.
I thank thee for thine aid, little one.
Yet to triumph with ease bringeth no glory.
How now? Wilt thou rise to my challenge?
I'vE no nEed fOr an iMperFect ForM...
Oh, what a lovely scent! Thank you ever so much!
What a wondrous perfume I will be able to fashion now!
'Tis a shame, but I'll simply have to acquire my blossoms through other means.
Bah! Winged monstrosities! Begone from this place!
Oh, no! I've gone and dropped all my blossoms!
Oh dear, oh dear! Whatever shall I do!?
It seems they've been drawn here by the flowers' most alluring aroma.
Oh, thank you! Now, to pick up all these blossoms...
And...yes, this flower is safe as well!
I have them all! Now to return and whip up the realm's most lovely perfume!
Oh, woe is me! Must I truly start all over again...?
How shall I ever face Overseer Sokles again?
I've only t-to fall to my knees. Beg for forgiveness!
Oh, thank you─I am saved, truly! I shall bring these to Overseer Sokles at once.
Should you happen upon any of those documents, do bring them to me.
Please, oh please, let this way lead out!
I just want to go home!
This hallway again!? Ugh, I need to get out of here!
There's nothing happy about this place!
Does an exit even exist here?
Confound it, where did everyone go...?
Please don't eat me! I'm all skin and bones!
O merciful Mrga, deliver us from evil!
Oh, praise be to the Mrga for sending you to me!
I'm on a pilgrimage to seek salvation from the gods.
But I became separated from my companions.
I will try and catch up to them now.
Thank you, and may the Mrga bless and keep you!
So much for the pilgrimage... Best flee while I can!
Uwaaah! Did you see the way that gaja looked at me!? It wants me for supper!
The beaches are overrun with those damn valras of late...
How am I supposed to go fishing with these blasted creatures about!? Am I doomed to starve to death?
Oh, thank you for dispatching those monsters! Finally I can fish again!
I suppose I'll put away my fishing pole and hope for better luck tomorrow...
Empty-handed again... The buyers at the market will be oh so disappointed in me...
We did it! They were no match for us!
Eheheh... This data is precisely what I needed!
Come─quickly! There's much work to be done!
We have to get everyone to safety!
Oh, you there! Familiar! Yes, you. Come here and give me a hand with something, won't you?
I'm looking for one who might do a bit of sparring against some creations to help spark my creativity. Are there truly none available for such a task?
I just need someone─anyone, really─to engage my aigokeros in combat. I must see how it performs when faced with an attacker.
Very well done, familiar, and thank you. I can sense great thoughts about to form... Any moment now...
Well, this isn't helping my creativity at all. Time to try a new tack.
It's as if I lack imagination enough to create anything at all.
Hmmm, this gives me much to consider.
No! I shall not fall before this beast!
There you all are! ...Hm? What's the matter?
The sacred site is just yonder, but there are too many fiends...
O benevolent Mrga, open the way for us!
This must be a trial... Yes, our faith is being tested.
Saved yet again! You have our gratitude!
Come, let us pray. O mighty Mrga...!
There... This leaves just the sea shrine, I believe.
Indeed. The end is in sight, my friends.
Let us stay focused to the last.
No... We've come too far to fall short like this...
This data will help me truly complete my masterpiece.
Oh, dear... What are you scheming now!?
Don't hold back now: give these robots your all! Eheheh...
If you'll excuse me, it's time to retreat...eheheh!
Go on─send these rowdy robots to the scrap heap!
Nothing ignites the imagination quite like a row. To that end, I shall pit you against an altogether different creature this time.
In fact, this is a variety I've only just recently registered with the bureau. Now then, show me what you can do!
Oh, I am flooded with inspiration. Visions of extraordinary concepts come upon me, the likes of which you would not believe!
Thank you, familiar. Your assistance proved most invaluable. How I look forward to the day I can share my new works with you!
I must put this to paper before I forget all that I have conjured.
Is this truly the limits of my imagination? Is there no method for me to improve upon my methods?
Alack, I am in desperate need of some inspiration.
INITIATING EXTERMINATION MODE. WEAKLINGS MUST PERISH!
And, er, if anyone can help me shut it down, that'd be swell!
Eheheh! Could someone lend me a hand?
Whew! That was far too close...
Eheheh! This has provided me with invaluable data.
My next order of business is cranking the output up to 300%!
Wh-What? That robot nearly killed you and that's your takeaway!?
If you'll excuse me, it's time to retreat...eheheh!
Don't be shy─turn my masterpiece into scrap metal!
EXTERMINATION MODE ACTIVATED. WEAKLINGS MUST PERISH!
Looks like we're safe for the time being.
Many thanks for your timely assistance!
Aye. The methods I'd researched prior to my defection...
Then it's true... So, where to next?
Let's search the facility at which I was stationed.
We may be able to glean vital information there.
Very well. I'll follow your lead.

No fiends here...
But what might this be?
Prepare to be awed by my masterpiece! But not too awed, mind you. You'll need your wits about you for this fight, I should think.
Long have I observed the creatures of this world, how they kill and maim, and at last, my studies bear fruit. Behold the product of my research!
O-Oh... This is not quite how I envisioned my concept. It was a great deal different on paper... At any rate─ Attack!
In my profession, that is what we call an abject failure. Perhaps I let my fancy carry me too far in the design phase... I will have to try, try again!
Well, this is all wrong. All wrong, indeed! How in goodness gracious did I come up with...this?
No, no, no. This is bad, so very bad...
Wh-What is it? H-How did it end up like that?
Where could I have gone so horribly wrong?
We won't let you get away this time!
This is it─the last stop on our pilgrimage. Come, let us pray!
Whew... As much devotion as we've shown, the Mrga have surely heard us.
To think that mortals could be so strong...
Could this be what the scriptures mean about being one's own light?
Relying not upon gods, but yourself to guide you...
Yes... Yes, that's it. What's important is our own will and determination.
So in the face of hardship, we should look not to the divine, but the strength within...
Precisely. If we are agreed, then let us walk this path together!
It's been a pleasure, my friends. Till next time, may all continue to strive for enlightenment!
My wee little nanka has returned to the sea! Oh, it brings a tear to the eye! Thank you, my friends!
Oh, dear...this isn't good. Come, my little one─we'd best head home.
Don't worry, we'll get out of this.
Bhujamga... Why did it have to be bhujamga?
Manusya have mercy, it's the man-eaters!
They could attack at any moment... What are we going to do!?
Now we can rest easy! Thank you!
Thank you for ridding me of those langurs! Now I can gather the herbs without fear.
Oh dear... Perhaps I should look for the herbs elsewhere...
Calm yourself. Focus, and picture it clearly in your mind's eye... Hellacious horns, rippling thew, a fearsome eye!
Behold, my greatest concept yet: the kyklops! Now, draw your weapon and succumb to a strength beyond measure!
Why...you defeated it! Goodness me, what an incredible familiar you are.
But rest assured, I have witnessed all most carefully, and see clearly what must be done to fix my creation. I shall return to Anamnesis Anyder and perform the final touches.
A very enlightening show that was, I must say.
I cannot rightly believe it. My creation─ It's won! Then perhaps this truly is the latest and greatest creature.
Though there is still much yet to be fine-tuned.
I believe in you, kyklops! You can do this.

Oh no, the crates...
OH NO, THE SPIDERS!

Do I have one in my hair!?
Please, someone help!

The nightmare is over...
Thank you!
M-Maybe we can round them up with lizards...or scorpions!
I thought those plants looked unfamiliar...
Hm. No more botanical studies today.
I've never seen anything like this!
And I'd rather my superiors not see it at all, if you catch my drift...
Thank you! I'll just...sweep these chunks away.
<sigh> I'd better start writing the incident report...
The laboratory calls! I shall be sure to make mention of you in my paper's footnotes!
So much time for such a paltry number of samples... No, I must return to my desk and rethink this entire research proposal!
Thanks to you, the truth is no longer out there! The bulk of it is back in my hands, and that's where I intend to keep it!
This is it. This is the end. Once word gets out that I lost these documents, the contract violation fines alone will be the death of me...
Let's make sure the next specimen is flora...
Transmission: Timely assistance requested. Stand by for details.
Unit designation: N-6205. Unit status: Attempting communications upgrade.
Unit directive: Establish contact with lost siege unit Chi and retrieve memory data.
Transmission: This unit requests the collection of scrap from other units and surrounding area for use in current mission.
Transmission: Sufficient materials obtained. Unit status: Commencing communications upgrade...
...Upgrade complete. This unit requests you stand by in case further assistance is required.
Transmission: Insufficient materials obtained. Aborting current mission.
Nooo! My precious merinos! All that luxurious wool...wasted!
You did it! You fought them off! Now my little merinos can safely return to chewing grass and growing wool!
That's it, my little one! You can do this!
Th-These have been illegally modified... We must stop them!
Transmission: Emergency assistance requested. Stand by for details.
Unit designation: N-6205. Unit status: Attempting to establish communications with siege unit Chi.
Unit directive: Establish contact with lost siege unit Chi and retrieve memory data.
Transmission: This unit is vulnerable while operating transceiver. Timely apprehension of hostiles requested.
Unit status: Communications established with siege unit Chi...
Transmission of current coordinates complete. Now awaiting siege unit's arrival. Stand by.
Activity detected on radar... Hostility confirmed.
This unit requests protection during transmission.
Unit designation: N-6205. Unit status: Anticipating imminent arrival of siege unit Chi.
Unit directive: Establish contact with lost siege unit Chi and retrieve memory data. Retrieval assistance requested.
...Update: This unit neglected to mention that said data is vital to our continued existence.
Reviewing siege protocol... Ah. Unit Chi's standing orders are to eliminate all unknown life-forms throughout the stars.
Analysis indicates that this would be unfortunate. Requesting combat support.
Uploading memory of defeat... This unit has never felt so alive.
Transmission: Chi systems confirmed non-operational. Downloading memory...
This data will be invaluable to our civilization. Gratitude output exceeding maximum levels...
We must gather the necessary components as swiftly as possible.
Oh gods, there's no stopping it now... Ebrelnaux!
The Sun does not heed the barking of feral dogs!
The farther we go, the worse this place gets...
Indeed. We'd best be prepared for any eventuality.
Were you able to find anything of note, Keltlona?
No such luck. It all looks like junk to me.
Alas, my search proved equally unproductive.
However, there's another location that is worth a try.
We are now close to the munitions factory.
That is where the automation process must've been carried out on older units.
And there is our welcoming party, right on cue.
It appears that was the last of the smaller units.
But they were no more than sub-units, or underlings, one might say.
The commanding unit should be nearby!
Correct. I believe it contains the components I require.
Excellent! You've succeeded in deactivating it!
Once I've retrieved the necessary parts, I'll make my way back to camp.
Soon, Garlemald will be free of automated magitek, and the people may reclaim their city.
A far more stubborn foe than anticipated. Let us retreat for the time being.
As this unit's directive has been fulfilled, this mission is complete.
Retrieved memory data will be analyzed for the further optimization of our protocols.
Sentimentality levels increasing... This unit bids farewell to you and its fallen comrade.
Apathy is no excuse to give up on living.
They lost their passion for everything? Even life itself?
That apathy could usurp their will to live is horrifying to say the least.
I pray such a future never comes to pass on Etheirys.
And so the world died without so much as a whimper.
Was this what brought about their end?
Our world will never succumb to such a fate.
Let us show Meteion what it means to have hope.
Was this meant to discourage us? Hmph.
They may have given up, but it's no reason for us to lose hope.
Show them what we're made of!
Another experiment gone wrong... How am I not surprised!?
Now then, the herbs should grow here...
Don't let them spit on the sheep!
This is like finding a needle in a haystack...
I don't see anything even close to what Ebrelnaux described.
There must be some hint as to the inner working of these automated weapons...
Please... Let there be something left!
It's no good. We'll have to abandon the search!
We'll never get past them at this rate.
Agreed. Let's regroup and think of another approach.
But whatever will I do about those langurs...?
Gah... My limbs refuse to move!
...And cleanse the corruption from our home!
By the grace of the elementals!
We've got to weather the storm!
Much obliged! Now let's give those pesky blighters what for!
How many malfunctions will it take for you to learn your lesson!?
I've never seen anything like this!
And I'd rather my superiors not see it at all, if you catch my drift...
Uwaaah! Did you see the way that gaja looked at me!? It wants me for supper!
The beaches are overrun with those damn valras of late...
How am I supposed to go fishing with these blasted creatures about!? Am I doomed to starve to death?
Don't worry, we'll get out of this.
Bhujamga... Why did it have to be bhujamga?
Manusya have mercy, it's the man-eaters!
They could attack at any moment... What are we going to do!?
I thought those plants looked unfamiliar...

Do I have one in my hair!?
Please, someone help!
For the honor of House Fortemps!
They'll win, I know they will!
By the light of the Crystal!
I shall not kneel before your fury!
Ugh... I cannot fight much longer...
We have to get away from here!
Make it stop! Make it stop!
Your compliance is not a factor.
We've come too far to fall short here!
A shower of amber to lay low my foes!
Rend? Nay, this shall more than suffice.
Would someone hurry up and heal me!?
I do have an image to uphold.
Slow. A sound choice, but slow.
By my true name, I shall consign all.
On my seat's honor, I shall protect all.
Well, back to it, I suppose.
What do you think of this?
Now, now, it's rude to interrupt.
Who? Me!? You can't be serious...
Is there nothing we can do!?
I can't believe what I'm seeing...
If this is what we must do...
I yield... Have mercy, I beg you...
Thordan!? Seven hells, he cannot mean to─!
Hmph, your compassion will be the end of you...
Will there never be peace between man and dragon...?
I would ask one last favor of you, Warrior of Light...
Now, while I have the beast subdued!
We must see Estinien to safety!
Vile dragons! My reign begins with your end!
In the name of King Thordan...
Go now! Before it's too late!

They may be shades,
but their blades are
just as deadly!
Don't be fools! Get away from here!
So this is the power of the Builder...
I'm sorry I cannot aid you in battle.
It seems Rhalgr awaits us above.
Yet more servants of the gods!?
Is it me or has Meteion grown a shade darker?
How many worlds have stained her soul with despair?
Meteion hath taken a blackened hue. To reflect her heart, mayhap?
Apathy...? Hmph, madness is what it was.
You'll not dissuade us with these bleak visions of the past.
Let us give the lie to her promise of ruin.
We can't afford to slow down!
Could that be...a Flood of Light!?
The world's fate doth rest on our shoulders...
What frightful presence doth assault my senses?
May thine end be without pain...
That nail could be trouble. Come, help me destroy it!
Doesn't it feel like we're being watched?
I don't... I don't want to die...
Guard my person, if you would!
Not so hasty, if you please!
Grrr, I am more than enough for your ilk!
That's as far as you go!
I will not fall to mortals!
Flee, or be feed for the fish.
Damn it! How do those little legs carry them so fast!?
If we don't do something, they're all going to get away!
Catch the rabbits, and the chickens will calm down for sure!
The chickens hold the bunnies at bay! Now's our chance!
Good gods! Never underestimate an angry chicken!
Look how calm the chickens are! They must be exhausted after all that.
There are still some stragglers. Let not a single bunny escape!
All right, my pretties. Back to the coop we go.
How are we supposed to catch these things?
Just try to stay with them as best you can!
We'll tear you to pieces, kupo!
All will tremble before my might!
Help is on the way, kupo!
Hearken to the song of my people!
Y-You're in for it now, kupo!
Bear witness to the power of kupo!
Hahaha! I've quite warmed to you!
Damn it, looks like the core is gone...
This armor won't be taking another step.
The rest is up to you, my friend. Take care!
Flee, damn you! Don't throw your lives away!
Hmph. Yours was always a vain struggle.
Nald, I leave them to you.
Is this the limit of mankind?
I will show you to the Underworld.
Behold. The lanterns ignite in the glyph's presence.
And thus we take our first step into the unknown.
This isle is where we find the vault's entrance?
Time to learn just how authentic our map truly is...
The glyph works its magic once more...
A bridge out of thin air...or cleverly hidden!
'Tis a rare breed of jellyfish─one with a sting, I imagine.
My, what dense aether this creature has.
This gelatinous eyesore bars our path.
'Tis a rare breed of jellyfish─one with a sting, I imagine.
Might that device be our sought-after “entrance”?

Shall we move on?
That looks to be a teleporter.

If only it had been a squid.
Imagine all the dried rations...

I'd rather not.
Oh look, is that a teleporter?

This must be the satrap's vault.
Such fascinating design...

Look!
We're deep under the Bounty!

The ocean floor...
The map was no fake after all.
Then our map was no fake after all.
I must needs memorize these defenses...
Judging by these defenses, we must be nearing the treasure!
We appear to have angered the vault guardians.
You are really quite serious about this consulting role of yours.
Hm. The key guardians appear mechanical in nature.
It will take more than this to halt our expedition.

A formidable-looking foe.
Be on your guard!
Please remember to heal whilst you take notes!

Attack routines, behavioral patterns...
There is much to report.
Another obstacle overcome! Now on to the next!
I only hope the Loporrits do not “misinterpret” the data.
Mountains of gold to dazzle the eye. Noted.
I assume we've reached the vault's inner chambers, then?
Aye...this should more than cover the price of the map.
How much did you pay for it, anyway?

Secret doors, hidden paths.
More elements to consider.
There are yet more rooms beyond!?
What other riches might this one vault hold?
Ere long, you shall be a veritable vault expert!

My head...
Is everyone all right?

Those silks...
Fashioned by alchemy, I suspect.
Keep your wits, and it's not so bad...

Again!?
Grrr, this is getting old!
Ulp... I think I might be sick...
The enchanted fabric saps our very strength.

Why can I not jump free?
Too much rich food of late...
He means to resurrect them again!
The least I expected from the one who defeated Zenos.
She can turn voidsent into crystal...
Go forth and smite my foes!
Isn't there a soul worth a damn in this castle!?
Your Light shall burn no more!
Your Light shall burn no more!
Time to put this technique to use!
This ought to do the trick!
A technique I honed on my adventures!
The mind is the only limit!
I'll get up as often as it takes!
Flames of judgment, blaze and burn!
Time to use my trump card!
